        "proof_hint": "Tap a comment to read it in full",
        "proof_item_1_short": "These are incredible.",
        "proof_item_1_full": "This product works incredible. The inside of my latex gloves are literally peeling off moist, just before I remove my hand from the DRYE liner dry to the touch. They really work. I have worn them for one week as a mechanic .  They are durable as they can be for being fabric. I take them off on my break and on lunch and I hang them up to dry and put them back on. After a couple days, I take them home and wash them. The science from the two separate layers is solid, the inner black layer never gets your hands moist. And the outer gray layer soaks everything up like a sponge. The longest that I have worn them is 2 to 3 hours straight. And still my hands stay dry.",
