        "proof_item_1_label": "Facebook",
        "proof_item_1_url": "",
        "proof_item_2_short": "Ordering my second pair right now.",
        "proof_item_2_full": "I have just gotten these last week and wore them for the first time today at work. These are incredible, nearly no more sweat in nitrile gloves, plus being so thin I barely notice them so this is definitely worth getting. I've been battling hyperhydrosis which only get worse with gloves I have to wear at work, so glad I found these, a few of my coworkers are looking into getting a few pairs themselves!",
