        "proof_item_3_short": "The liners have been a huge help",
        "proof_item_3_full": "I'm an automotive painter in Phoenix and was having terrible sweat issues wearing nitrile gloves during the summer months. The liners have been a huge help — I'm no longer dripping sweat on my paint jobs and my hands feel better.",
