        "proof_item_4_handle": "@dsmmaster2003",
        "proof_item_4_label": "Instagram comment",
        "proof_item_4_url": "",
        "proof_item_5_short": "They do a great job keeping sweat off my hands ",
        "proof_item_5_full": "I mainly use these for car detailing. The slim thickness gives great dexterity, but after about two hours under gloves, it can feel a bit damp. The stitching ripped once, but that might’ve been my fault. They do a great job keeping sweat off my hands — even when slightly wet, they still work. I just wash and reuse them again.",
